<span id="freeTextContainer18276520206858378955"><strong>Intimate and intriguing telling</strong><br/><br/>Thoroughly researched narrative of three parties&apos; tragic encounter with Hurricane Lenny. Filled with John&apos;s signature subtle humor and pragmatism, and an even more fascinating read as you begin to understand his deep connection with Carl. The author&apos;s salesmanship and subject matter expertise makes for a fascinating read as he often understands the subjects&apos; behavior end conditions better than they did themselves.</span>
  <span id="freeText18276520206858378955" style="display:none"><strong>Intimate and intriguing telling</strong><br /><br />Thoroughly researched narrative of three parties' tragic encounter with Hurricane Lenny. Filled with John's signature subtle humor and pragmatism, and an even more fascinating read as you begin to understand his deep connection with Carl. The author's salesmanship and subject matter expertise makes for a fascinating read as he often understands the subjects' behavior end conditions better than they did themselves.</span>
